Package org.blockchainnative.metadata

Class ContractInfo<TContractType,TMethodInfo extends MethodInfo,TEventInfo extends EventInfo<?,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.blockchainnative.metadata.ContractInfo<TContractType,TMethodInfo,TEventInfo>
  • Type Parameters:
    TContractType - smart contract interface type
    TMethodInfo - Concrete type of the MethodInfo objects used by ContractInfo
    TEventInfo - Concrete type of the EventInfo objects used by ContractInfo
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EthereumContractInfo, FabricContractInfo
    public class ContractInfo<TContractType,TMethodInfo extends MethodInfo,TEventInfo extends EventInfo<?,?>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds all relevant information about smart contract interfaces in order to allow implementations of ContractWrapperGenerator to generate a functioning wrapper class.

    It is recommended to use ContractInfoBuilder and its subtypes to construct instances of this class.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    ContractInfoBuilder, ContractWrapperGenerator
